6:["$","h3",null,{"children":"Introducing the Prisma™ Analytical Framework"}]
7:["$","p",null,{"children":"Prisma™ is a Metaratus® proprietary analytical framework designed to bring clarity to the complexity of the Post-COVID, AI Era™. Inspired by the physical behavior of a prism, the framework using formal logical reasoning principles to isolate the variables under consideration in a business optimization environment for the purpose of “refracting” multifaceted business challenges into their individual constituent components, allowing decision-makers to better observe and understand the underlying structure, causality, and interdependence of competing outcomes with greater precision and decision-making clarity."}]
8:["$","h3",null,{"children":"Refracting Complexity into Variables"}]
9:["$","p",null,{"children":"Rather than treating challenges as monolithic problems, which we have observed is often the status quo used in corporate environments, Prisma™ deconstructs every obstacle into its underlying economic, operational, behavioral, technological, and strategic variables using propositional logic, abductive reasoning, and inferential analysis for the purpose of distinguishing between the aggravating factors that a causal to the unwanted outcomes being experienced. By examining how these variables interact, reinforce, or constrain one another, our Consulting framework aids organizations gain a more accurate understanding of what is truly driving, or preventing, their desired outcomes."}]
a:["$","h3",null,{"children":"Structured Analysis, Not Abstract Insight"}]
b:["$","p",null,{"children":"Prisma™ is a structured analytical discipline that combines business consulting expertise with AI tools and insights to model relationships that often involve surface hidden dependencies in a manner that enables us to test strategic assumptions. This is akin to using the scientific method to test the null hypothesis, but, in this case, we are applying it business settings in a manner that was never possible before the advent of AI. Conceptually, we view AI environments as our thought laboratory, as they enable us to run scenario analysis based upon illimitable logical tests that we can apply to a client’s business model. The result is comprehensive, Humanocentric™ analysis that is both rooted in seasoned experience and enhanced by AI capabilities, thereby enabling Metaratus® to provide clients with cutting-edge AI Consulting services, while still remaining accessible and cultivating a deep understanding of each client’s business model."}]
c:["$","h3",null,{"children":"A Framework for the Post-COVID, AI Era™"}]
d:["$","p",null,{"children":"In an environment shaped by the intersecting vectors of global disruption and accelerated technological change, organizations require seasoned human intuition in conjunction with the latest AI technology. Prisma™ provides a repeatable framework for circumnavigating uncertainty: by creating a Humanocentric™ balancing point that combines our sapience with the data processing capabilities of AI, Metaratus® supports disciplined thinking, informed decision-making, and resilient execution in the Post-COVID, AI Era™, a period of history in which we are actively writing the next chapter."}]
